    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not just a setback though. it's the core of who i am. i built my whole identity around this theory. now that i know it's garbage, there's no version of me that works anymore. the person i was is just... gone. i look in the mirror and i don't even see a person, just a mistake. it feels like i've been living a life that isn't even mine.",
